hero_title.text: Hello, my name is Graeme Fraser. I am a full-stack web developer.

about_bio.text: Hello, my name is Graeme and I am a full-stack web developer. I am working at Places4Students where I have helped develop a house rental .NET Core website by programming in the front-end and back-end.

I am currently in the Computer Programmer Analyst program at Niagara College where I’ve studied database, web and software development techniques. Through a school opportunity, I  have also helped create a messaging app for a non-profit organization with a team of students.
In my spare time, I enjoy staying active by playing basketball and volleyball.
